<li class='cover' id='bookCover_2350981'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/2350981.The_Perfect_Plan"><img alt="The Perfect Plan" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1344648923l/2350981._SX98_.jpg" />
